bels-that-show-speeds-fees-and-data-allowances-103832369.html"><ins>互联网服务提供商推出强制性宽带“营养”标签，显示速度、费用和数据限额</ins></a></p><p><em>​​您可以每天将这些报告直接发送到您的收件箱。</em><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/about/newsletter/"><em>在这里订阅！</em></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-photos-enhanced-editing-tools-will-no-longer-require-a-subscription-160015336.html">Google Photos的增强编辑工具将不再需要订阅</a></h2><h3>Magic Eraser、Photo UnBlur、Magic Editor 等将于五月广泛推出。</h3><h3></h3><p>免费的 Google Photos 用户无需每年支付 20 美元以上即可获得增强的编辑功能。这意味着所有用户都将获得一些 Google 人工智能驱动的工具，例如 Photo UnBlur、Magic Eraser 和 Magic Editor。我可以证明：在拍摄幼儿照片时，Photo UnBlur 可以改变游戏规则。不是。停留。仍然。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-photos-enhanced-editing-tools-will-no-longer-require-a-subscription-160015336.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-grab-the-nothing-phone-2-for-74-off-right-now-210527323.html">Nothing Phone 2 再减 74 美元</a></h2><h3>它适用于 T-Mobile 和 AT&amp;T 的网络。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-grab-the-nothing-phone-2-for-74-off-right-now-210527323.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-04/96d49200-f7ec-11ee-aef3-51e3ad538a01" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-04/96d49200-f7ec-11ee-aef3-51e3ad538a01" style="height:405px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="0be1eb5a-aa95-30c6-a0b2-63d710c54df2"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure></a><p>亚马逊自推出 Nothing Phone 2 以来首次进行促销。这款另类的主流智能手机替代品比平时价格低 74 美元，降至 625 美元。该交易包括具有 12GB RAM 和 256GB 存储空间的版本，并且可以在 T-Mobile 或 AT&amp;T 上激活。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-grab-the-nothing-phone-2-for-74-off-right-now-210527323.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-survivors-hits-playstation-this-summer-174515287.html">《吸血鬼幸存者》今年夏天登陆 PlayStation</a></h2><h3>该游戏还将在 5 月推出魂斗罗 DLC。</h3><h3></h3><p>热门复古子弹地狱 Rogue 风格的《<em>吸血鬼幸存者</em>》即将登陆 PlayStation——这可能是它尚未登陆的唯一平台。该游戏还将在 5 月 9 日推出一批跨界 DLC <em>。《吸血鬼幸存者：枪械行动》</em>带来了<em>魂斗罗</em>角色和武器，所以期待更多的枪支。事实上，其中有 22 个。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-survivors-hits-playstation-this-summer-174515287.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-amazon-stops-paying-bonuses-to-alexa-developers-111557415.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-amazon-stops-paying-bonuses-to-alexa-developers-111557415.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cd7b89c1-a553-402b-b821-a31af9a10a96 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mat Smith]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 11 Apr 2024 11:15:57 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1712831112</ingested><modified> 2024-04-11T10:25:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="840" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-09%2Fcd527400-57c9-11ee-99f9-de472f0c3bee&amp;resize=1400%2C840&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b383431ed24de122ce56cd7d4eae03eb817ced12" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media