>接着分享了有关该<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-nso-group-spyware-lawsuit-181306004.html">事件</a>的更多信息。 “由于你是谁或你做了什么，这种攻击很可能专门针对你。尽管在检测此类攻击时永远不可能达到绝对确定性，但苹果公司对此警告充满信心 - 请认真对待，”警报继续说道。苹果解释说，它无法提供任何有关引发该消息的信息，因为担心额外的信息将帮助攻击者避免将来被发现。该公司利用内部信息和调查来查明攻击。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这并不是<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-and-google-are-probably-spying-on-your-push-notifications-154543184.html">苹果</a>第一次不得不发送此类通知。自 2021 年以来，150 多个国家的个人收到了类似的信息，包括去年 10 月向<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-reportedly-faces-pressure-in-india-after-sending-out-warnings-of-state-sponsored-hacking-073036597.html">印度</a>的一些记者和政界人士发出的警告。然而，目前尚不清楚哪些国家/地区的个人收到了警报。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/iphone-users-in-92-countries-received-a-spyware-attack-warning-from-apple-104554943.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/iphone-users-in-92-countries-received-a-spyware-attack-warning-from-apple-104554943.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 11fca525-516c-4a74-ae19-f74360be5c26 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sarah Fielding]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:45:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1712828463</ingested><modified> 2024-04-11T09:41:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="932" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-04%2F4e11fb10-f22f-11ee-9fef-15e53f1ebc5d&amp;resize=1400%2C932&amp;client=19